name: LOL: Last One Laughing
overview: An unscripted variety series from Mexico in which ten professional comedians compete for a cash prize by trying to make each other laugh. The one who refrains from laughing the longest, while forcing other contestants to laugh first, is the winner.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Eugenio Derbez kicks off the exciting second season of LOL with a new cast of contenders. Lots of changes and pressure is on, as the battle to keep a straight face and win the million pesos begins.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: New comedians, more laughs and a bunch of new characters will try (and succeed) in breaking the limits of comedy on the third season of LOL Mexico. A competition between ten comedians locked inside a house where the only thing that's not allowed is to laugh.

seasons.name: Season 4
seasons.overview: What is the best tool to make a comedian laugh? Another comedian! That is why comedians won't be playing on their own in this fourth season. Instead, they will be joined by their best comedian friends to compete in DUOS, each willing to do whatever it takes to make the other DUOS laugh and ultimately earn LOL's trophy, arguably the most coveted comedy award EVER.

episodes.name: The First Ten
episodes.overview: Eugenio Derbez surprises the comedians with invitations to the competition. They are confused, excited, and nervous. Will each of them accept, or be too scared to participate, not knowing who their competitors will be? Our comedians enter the house one by one, and the first ever competition of LOL begins.

episodes.name: The Puppet Master
episodes.overview: After Eugenio hands out another yellow card to one of the comedians, El Escorpión Dorado reveals a new look. Others begin to bring out their props and costumes to raise the stakes within the house as Eugenio distributes more yellow cards amongst the comedians. A new toy is introduced, Finally, a comedian is eliminated after a red card is handed out.

episodes.name: A Shocking Surprise
episodes.overview: Everybody becomes nervous after the first red card. With nine comedians left in the house, Alex attempts to "spice" things up. An electrifying surprise gets delivered - will the comedians be up for this shocking challenge? An explosive ending to a story shakes up the house, but will it be enough to cause more comedians to be eliminated?

episodes.name: Another type of Christmas Story
episodes.overview: With less than three hours left in the competition, some of the comedians get into the Christmas spirit, and decide to act out a very "special" pastoral, but it's far from what is typically taught in Sunday school. Some of the comedians have too much fun during a party game and accidentally lose focus, resulting in Eugenio stepping in to eliminate them from the house.

episodes.name: Drown me with Jack
episodes.overview: The competition is becoming more tough, as the remaining comedians try push each other's boundaries with new tactics to make the others laugh. With less than two hours left, a special guest finally reveals herself from the locker room. Eugenio eliminates another comedian from the house.

episodes.name: It Tastes like Chocolate
episodes.overview: Less than one hour is left, and those in the house are under so much pressure, that they begin to lose their minds. One of them reveals a delicious dessert that comes with a tasty surprise, as others pull out all of the stops to eliminate their remaining competitors, resulting in a head to head showdown with the final two. When the clock ticks down to zero, who will walk away a millionaire?

episodes.name: A New Beginning
episodes.overview: Eugenio Derbez kicks off the exciting second season of LOL with a new cast of contenders. Lots of changes and pressure is on, as the battle to keep a straight face and win the million pesos begins.

episodes.name: Shame or Shine
episodes.overview: The temptation to laugh heats up as the competitors bring out hilarious new antics. Eugenio hands out yellow cards.

episodes.name: Who is Next?
episodes.overview: As Eugenio hands out more yellow cards and this time the house experiences a card that nobody saw coming.

episodes.name: No One is Safe
episodes.overview: Seven competitors left in the house when Eugenio pulls out the most surprising cards of the season yet!

episodes.name: A Hairy Situation
episodes.overview: The comedians face off in an attempt to bring out laughs and eliminate more competition. A magical performance on stage surprises everyone with a disappearing act you’ll never forget!

episodes.name: No Limits to Win
episodes.overview: The pressure to win drives the comedians to new lengths, throwing their dignity aside to risk it all for a million pesos.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: Eugenio Derbez kicks off the exciting second season of LOL with a new cast of contenders. Lots of changes and pressure is on, as the battle to keep a straight face and win the million pesos begins.

episodes.name: Ready For The Third Round
episodes.overview: New comedians, more laughs and a bunch of new characters will try to break the limits of comedy on the third season of LOL. A competition between ten comedians locked inside a house where the only thing that's not allowed is to laugh.

episodes.name: Poop-a-strophic
episodes.overview: The fight not to laugh is getting more complicated. A dance competition is organized inside a gay party and some comedians show their best techniques within the world of music, drama, and poop.

episodes.name: Go Big Or Go Home
episodes.overview: It's time to do some trimming and we're not only talking about facial hair. The winner will be the one who makes the biggest bet... or not.

episodes.name: The Laughs Under Pressure
episodes.overview: The clock is ticking and the pressure is on to act fast. If not, the comedians are at risk of passive play.

episodes.name: An Unexpected New Rule
episodes.overview: Niurka meets Stephen Hawking and an unexpected new rule is introduced, leaving the comedians in shock.

episodes.name: No Second Chances
episodes.overview: The comedians inside the house as well as the time left to play the game are coming to an end. A whirlwind of emotions, tears, sweat and poop have led us to this moment: The Winner of LOL Mexico 3.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: New comedians, more laughs and a bunch of new characters will try (and succeed) in breaking the limits of comedy on the third season of LOL Mexico. A competition between ten comedians locked inside a house where the only thing that's not allowed is to laugh.

episodes.name: Double Or Nothing
episodes.overview: And we're off to a rough start! Cards are quickly earned on this season.

episodes.name: Laughter Is Served
episodes.overview: Sometimes ammunition is so strong, friendly fire happens.

episodes.name: Gone With The Dignity
episodes.overview: If you think you've seen it all, nah…

episodes.name: Fire From Behind
episodes.overview: Rules are meant to be broken, right? Wrong. On this house breaking the rules get's you a card.

episodes.name: Where's The Limit?
episodes.overview: That's got to hurt. A lot. Probably. Definitely.

episodes.name: And For My Final Act… Shots
episodes.overview: Final lap. The finish line is near. This will be a photo finish!
